# Runtime files (auto-generated)
*.dll.config
*.runtimeconfig.json
*.deps.json
*.ni.dll
*.pdb
*.xml
*.json   # ⚠️ 谨慎：仅忽略生成的 json（如 swagger.json），主配置如 appsettings.json 应提交

# ==============================
# 📦 NuGet & Package Management
# ==============================
packages/
.nuget/
NuGet.Config          # 可选：若需私有源配置可提交；否则忽略
global-packages/      # 用户级缓存，绝不可提交
~/.nuget/             # 全局路径，不应出现在 repo 中

